    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 股价飙升，催生三位亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/nvidia-s-remarkable-stock-surge-mints-three-board-billionaires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 的辉煌一年让首席执行官黄仁勋的净资产达到了新的高度。该公司还让三位任职时间最长的董事会成员跻身亿万富翁行列，创造了几乎前所未闻的财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/nvidia-s-remarkable-stock-surge-mints-three-board-billionaires</guid>
